        "- `PROTECT` — you're in the top 20%, or your bankroll is below £30k → widen spreads, minimise risk\n",
        "- `BALANCED` — middle of the pack → use default quote tiers\n",
        "- `CATCH_UP` — bottom 30% → tighten spreads, try to win market maker\n",
        "\n",
        "`decide_trade` — given the market maker's bid/ask and your fair value, returns:\n",
        "- **Direction**: BUY if fair_value > maker_ask (you think it's worth more than they're asking), SELL if maker_bid > fair_value\n",
        "- **Shares**: Quarter-Kelly position sizing — scales with your edge and your current bankroll; always at least 10 (the forced minimum)\n",
        "- Falls back to minimum 10-share trade when edge is too small to justify a larger position\n",
        "\n",
